  mpd-0.12.0_rc1.ebuild, mpd-0.12.0_rc2.ebuild, mpd-0.12.0_rc3.ebuild:
  Block sys-cluster/mpich2, since it also installs /usr/bin/mpd and
  /etc/mpd.conf. Bug #145367.

