*mpd-0.11.2-r1 (22 Jul 2004)

  22 Jul 2004; Brian Harring <ferringb@gentoo.org> mpd-0.10.3-r1.ebuild,
  mpd-0.10.4.ebuild, mpd-0.11.2.ebuild, mpd-0.9.4-r1.ebuild, mpd-0.11.2-r1.ebuild:
